The '''Reena Trade Route''' was a [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]] [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperlane]] that spun off the [[Corellian Run/Legends|Corellian Run]] at [[Druckenwell/Legends|Druckenwell]], going as far as [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. It passed through five [[Sector/Legends|sectors]].

During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], bribery on nearby planets by [[Zann Consortium/Legends|Zann Consortium]]-affiliated [[defiler]]s led to information&mdash;and piracy&mdash;on the trade route.<ref name="foc">''[[Star Wars: Empire at War: Forces of Corruption]]''</ref>

